text: Pyatiletka () is a rural locality (a village) in Austrumsky Selsoviet, Iglinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 238 as of 2010. == Geography == It is located 50 km from Iglino, 14 km from Austrum. == References == Category:Rural localities in Iglinsky District
title: Pyatiletka, Austrumsky Selsoviet, Iglinsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
